{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"A month ago today"},{"time":2000,"text":"I stood there:"},{"time":4000,"text":"90 degrees south, the top of"},{"time":6000,"text":"the bottom of the world, the Geographic South Pole."},{"time":8000,"text":"And I stood there beside two very good friends of mine,"},{"time":11000,"text":"Richard Weber and Kevin Vallely."},{"time":13000,"text":"Together we had just broken the world speed record"},{"time":16000,"text":"for a trek to the South Pole."},{"time":18000,"text":"It took us 33 days,"},{"time":20000,"text":"23 hours and 55 minutes to get there."},{"time":24000,"text":"We shaved five days off the previous best time."},{"time":28000,"text":"And in the process, I became the first person in history"},{"time":31000,"text":"to make the entire 650-mile journey,"},{"time":33000,"text":"from Hercules Inlet to South Pole,"},{"time":36000,"text":"solely on feet, without skis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"Now, many of you are probably saying, \"Wait a sec,"},{"time":41000,"text":"is this tough to do?\""},{"time":44000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":45000,"text":"Imagine, if you will,"},{"time":47000,"text":"dragging a sled, as you just saw in that video clip,"},{"time":49000,"text":"with 170 pounds of gear,"},{"time":52000,"text":"in it everything you need to survive on your Antarctic trek."},{"time":55000,"text":"It's going to be 40 below, every single day."},{"time":57000,"text":"You'll be in a massive headwind."},{"time":59000,"text":"And at some point you're going to have to cross these cracks in the ice,"},{"time":62000,"text":"these crevasses."},{"time":64000,"text":"Some of them have a very precarious thin footbridge underneath them"},{"time":67000,"text":"that could give way at a moment's notice,"},{"time":69000,"text":"taking your sled, you, into the abyss, never to be seen again."},{"time":74000,"text":"The punchline to your journey? Look at the horizon."},{"time":77000,"text":"Yes, it's uphill the entire way,"},{"time":79000,"text":"because the South Pole is at 10,000 feet,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and you're starting at sea level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"Our journey did not, in fact, begin at Hercules Inlet,"},{"time":87000,"text":"where frozen ocean meets the land of Antarctica."},{"time":90000,"text":"It began a little less than two years ago."},{"time":92000,"text":"A couple of buddies of mine and I"},{"time":94000,"text":"had finished a 111-day run across the entire Sahara desert."},{"time":98000,"text":"And while we were there we learned"},{"time":100000,"text":"the seriousness of the water crisis in Northern Africa."},{"time":103000,"text":"We also learned that many of the issues facing the people of Northern Africa"},{"time":106000,"text":"affected young people the most."},{"time":110000,"text":"I came home to my wife after 111 days of running in the sand,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and I said, \"You know, there's no doubt if this bozo can get across the desert,"},{"time":116000,"text":"we are capable of doing anything we set our minds to.\""},{"time":120000,"text":"But if I'm going to continue doing these adventures, there has to be"},{"time":122000,"text":"a reason for me to do them"},{"time":124000,"text":"beyond just getting there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"Around that time I met an extraordinary human being,"},{"time":130000,"text":"Peter Thum, who inspired me with his actions."},{"time":132000,"text":"He's trying to find and solve water issues, the crisis around the world."},{"time":136000,"text":"His dedication inspired me to come up with this expedition:"},{"time":139000,"text":"a run to the South Pole"},{"time":141000,"text":"where, with an interactive website,"},{"time":143000,"text":"I will be able to bring young people, students and teachers from around the world"},{"time":146000,"text":"on board the expedition with me,"},{"time":148000,"text":"as active members."},{"time":150000,"text":"So we would have a live website, that every single day of the 33 days,"},{"time":154000,"text":"we would be blogging, telling stories of,"},{"time":157000,"text":"you know, depleted ozone forcing us to cover our faces,"},{"time":160000,"text":"or we will burn."},{"time":163000,"text":"Crossing miles and miles of sastrugi --"},{"time":165000,"text":"frozen ice snowdrifts that could be hip-deep."},{"time":169000,"text":"I'm telling you, crossing these things with 170-pound sled,"},{"time":171000,"text":"that sled may as well have weighed 1,700 pounds,"},{"time":173000,"text":"because that's what it felt like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"We were blogging to this live website daily"},{"time":177000,"text":"to these students that were tracking us as well,"},{"time":179000,"text":"about 10-hour trekking days,"},{"time":181000,"text":"15-hour trekking days,"},{"time":183000,"text":"sometimes 20 hours of trekking daily to meet our goal."},{"time":188000,"text":"We'd catch cat-naps at 40 below on our sled, incidentally."},{"time":192000,"text":"In turn, students,"},{"time":194000,"text":"people from around the world, would ask us questions."},{"time":196000,"text":"Young people would ask the most amazing questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"One of my favorite: It's 40 below, you've got to go to the bathroom,"},{"time":202000,"text":"where are you going to go and how are you going to do it?"},{"time":204000,"text":"I'm not going to answer that. But I will answer some of the more popular questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"Where do you sleep? We slept in a tent that was very low to the ground,"},{"time":211000,"text":"because the winds on Antarctica were so extreme, it would blow anything else away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"What do you eat? One of my favorite dishes on expedition:"},{"time":218000,"text":"butter and bacon. It's about a million calories."},{"time":221000,"text":"We were burning about 8,500 a day,"},{"time":223000,"text":"so we needed it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"How many batteries do you carry for all the equipment that you have?"},{"time":229000,"text":"Virtually none. All of our equipment, including film equipment,"},{"time":232000,"text":"was charged by the sun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"And do you get along? I certainly hope so,"},{"time":237000,"text":"because at some point or another on this expedition,"},{"time":239000,"text":"one of your teammates is going to have to take a very big needle,"},{"time":241000,"text":"and put it in an infected blister, and drain it for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244000,"text":"But seriously, seriously, we did get along,"},{"time":247000,"text":"because we had a common goal of wanting to inspire these young people."},{"time":250000,"text":"They were our teammates! They were inspiring us."},{"time":253000,"text":"The stories we were hearing got us to the South Pole."},{"time":257000,"text":"The website worked brilliantly as a two-way street of communication."},{"time":260000,"text":"Young people in northern Canada, kids in an elementary school,"},{"time":263000,"text":"dragging sleds across the school-yard,"},{"time":266000,"text":"pretending they were Richard, Ray and Kevin. Amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"We arrived at the South Pole. We huddled into that tent,"},{"time":273000,"text":"45 below that day, I'll never forget it."},{"time":276000,"text":"We looked at each other with these looks"},{"time":279000,"text":"of disbelief at what we had just completed."},{"time":283000,"text":"And I remember looking at the guys thinking,"},{"time":285000,"text":"\"What do I take from this journey?\" You know? Seriously."},{"time":288000,"text":"That I'm this uber-endurance guy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"As I stand here today talking to you guys,"},{"time":294000,"text":"I've been running for the grand sum of five years."},{"time":296000,"text":"And a year before that I was a pack-a-day smoker,"},{"time":300000,"text":"living a very sedentary lifestyle."},{"time":302000,"text":"What I take from this journey, from my journeys,"},{"time":305000,"text":"is that, in fact,"},{"time":307000,"text":"within every fiber of my belief standing here,"},{"time":310000,"text":"I know that we can make the impossible possible."},{"time":313000,"text":"I'm learning this at 40."},{"time":316000,"text":"Can you imagine? Seriously, can you imagine?"},{"time":320000,"text":"I'm learning this at 40 years of age."},{"time":322000,"text":"Imagine being 13 years old,"},{"time":324000,"text":"hearing those words, and believing it."},{"time":327000,"text":"Thank you very much. Thank you."},{"time":329000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}